(107, 69, 'Gà quay tiêu', '<h4 id=\"bkmrk-nguy%E3%AAn-li%E1%BB%87u%3A\"><strong>Nguyên liệu:</strong></h4>\r\n<ul id=\"bkmrk-%E4%90u%EC%80i-ga%EC%80%2C-ca%EC%81nh-ga%EC%80-%28pha%EC%82%EC\">\r\n<li>Đùi gà, cánh gà (phần gà nào cũng được)</li>\r\n<li>Tỏi, hành khô, ớt kim</li>\r\n<li>Sốt : Nước mắm, đường, tương cà, tương ớt, hạt tiêu xay</li>\r\n<li>Tiêu sọ đen</li>\r\n<li>Dầu điều (không bắt buộc) - có thể thay thế bằng bột ớt (mục đích giúp màu đẹp hơn)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-\"><a href=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/uploads/images/gallery/2022-04/pha-sot-va-uop-ga.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/uploads/images/gallery/2022-04/scaled-1680-/pha-sot-va-uop-ga.jpg\" alt=\"pha-sot-va-uop-ga.jpg\" width=\"145\" height=\"145\"></a><a href=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/uploads/images/gallery/2022-04/nuong-ga-4.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/uploads/images/gallery/2022-04/scaled-1680-/nuong-ga-4.jpg\" alt=\"nuong-ga-4.jpg\" width=\"145\" height=\"145\"></a><a href=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/uploads/images/gallery/2022-04/thanh-pham-384.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8000/uploads/images/gallery/2022-04/scaled-1680-/thanh-pham-384.jpg\" alt=\"thanh-pham-384.jpg\" width=\"147\" height=\"147\"></a></p>\r\n<h4 id=\"bkmrk-c%E3%A1ch-l%E3%A0m%3A\"><strong>Cách làm:</strong></h4>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk-1.-ga%EC%80-ru%EC%9B%EC%89a-sa%EC%A3ch-sau\">1. Gà rửa sạch sau đó để ráo. Hành, tỏi đập dập. Ướp gà với hành, tỏi và phần sốt : Có thời gian nên ướp gà trước khoảng 3-4 tiếng hoặc qua đêm và sau đó cho gia vị vào<br>2. Sau đó nướng gà ở 200 độ trong vòng 45p. Phần nước thịt khi nướng xong có thể dùng để chấm gà hoặc ăn với cơm.</p>\r\n<h4 id=\"bkmrk-%E1%BA%A2nh-minh-h%E1%BB%8Da\"><strong>Ảnh minh họa</strong></h4>\r\n<p id=\"bkmrk--0\"